WEBVTT

00:00:14.785 --> 00:00:23.335 line:90% position:50% align:center
My mom works hard ev’ry day.
She takes good care of me.

00:00:23.335 --> 00:00:31.719 line:90% position:50% align:center
We always find time to pray.
It makes us happy.

00:00:31.719 --> 00:00:39.643 line:90% position:50% align:center
My heart is full of love
In my family of three.

00:00:40.603 --> 00:00:53.073 line:90% position:50% align:center
Together, we can do anything—
Jehovah, my mom, and me.

00:01:00.039 --> 00:01:08.797 line:90% position:50% align:center
Before we both go to bed,
We read Bible stories.

00:01:08.797 --> 00:01:17.056 line:90% position:50% align:center
Timothy’s my fav’rite
’Cause he’s just like me.

00:01:17.056 --> 00:01:25.856 line:90% position:50% align:center
His mom taught him the truth
And made him firm in his beliefs.

00:01:25.856 --> 00:01:38.911 line:90% position:50% align:center
Like Timothy, I have what I need—
Jehovah, my mom, and me.

00:01:45.918 --> 00:02:00.140 line:90% position:50% align:center
What can I do with a gift so great?
I can listen carefully.

00:02:03.477 --> 00:02:22.079 line:90% position:50% align:center
Every day I can show I appreciate my family—
Jehovah, my mom, and me.

